# Arac Alis Satis Takip

Tarayicida dogrudan acilan, arac alim-satim surecini takip etmek icin hazirlanmis hafif bir uygulama.

## Ozellikler

- Arac bilgileri, alis ve satis tarihleri ile kayit ekleme
- Masraf dahil net kar zarar hesabi
- Stokta, beklemede ve satildi durumlari
- Arama, filtreleme ve siralama
- CSV disa aktarma
- Verileri tarayici `localStorage` uzerinde saklama

## Kullanim

`index.html` dosyasini tarayicida acman yeterli.

## Dosyalar

- `index.html`: arayuz iskeleti
- `styles.css`: tasarim ve responsive duzen
- `app.js`: kayit, hesaplama ve tablo mantigi

:root {
  --bg: #f3efe8;
  --surface: #fffdf9;
  --surface-strong: #ffffff;
  --ink: #1f1c18;
  --muted: #675f56;
  --line: #ddd2c4;
  --brand: #2f6c4d;
  --brand-soft: #d8ebe0;
  --accent: #b4682d;
  --accent-soft: #f5e3d5;
  --danger: #b1483e;
  --danger-soft: #f4ddd8;
  --info: #365f70;
  --info-soft: #d9e8ee;
  --shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(52, 41, 28, 0.08);
  --radius: 8px;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html,
body {
  margin: 0;
  min-height: 100%;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--ink);
  font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
}

body {
  line-height: 1.45;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

button,
input,
select,
textarea {
  font: inherit;
}

.page-shell {
  max-width: 1480px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 24px;
}

.hero-band {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(320px, 0.8fr);
  gap: 24px;
  padding: 28px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f1e7 0%, #fffdf9 55%, #eef5f1 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.16);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.eyebrow,
.section-kicker,
.meta-label {
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.hero-band h1,
.panel h2,
.subheading h3 {
  margin: 0;
  letter-spacing: 0;
}

.hero-band h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  max-width: 14ch;
}

.hero-copy {
  margin: 14px 0 0;
  max-width: 62ch;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.hero-meta {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 14px;
  align-self: stretch;
}

.hero-meta > div {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  min-height: 110px;
  padding: 18px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  border: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.16);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}

.hero-band > div {
  min-width: 0;
}

.hero-meta strong {
  font-size: 1.02rem;
}

.app-shell {
  display: grid;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 24px;
}

.summary-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 14px;
}

.summary-card {
  min-height: 132px;
  padding: 18px;
  background: var(--surface-strong);
  border: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.16);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.summary-card.positive {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-strong), #f5fbf8);
}

.summary-card.warning {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-strong), #fff8f1);
}

.summary-card.info {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-strong), #f5fafc);
}

.summary-label {
  margin: 0 0 18px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.summary-value {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 1.85rem);
  word-break: break-word;
}

.summary-note {
  margin: 10px 0 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
}

.workspace-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(360px, 0.92fr) minmax(0, 1.38fr);
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: start;
}

.panel {
  min-width: 0;
  padding: 24px;
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.16);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.panel-heading {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.panel-note,
.subheading p {
  margin: 6px 0 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  max-width: 34ch;
}

.vehicle-form {
  display: grid;
  gap: 18px;
}

.form-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  gap: 16px;
}

.form-grid label {
  display: grid;
  gap: 8px;
}

.form-grid label span {
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.form-grid input,
.form-grid select,
.form-grid textarea,
.toolbar input,
.toolbar select {
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 46px;
  padding: 10px 12px;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  background: var(--surface-strong);
  color: var(--ink);
}

.form-grid textarea {
  resize: vertical;
  min-height: 112px;
}

.sale-field,
.notes-field {
  grid-column: span 2;
}

.form-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 120px;
  min-height: 44px;
  padding: 0 16px;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform 140ms ease, background-color 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease;
}

.button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.button.primary {
  background: var(--brand);
  color: #fff;
}

.button.secondary {
  background: var(--accent-soft);
  border-color: #dfc0a6;
  color: #79451b;
}

.button.ghost {
  background: transparent;
  border-color: var(--line);
  color: var(--ink);
}

.button.delete {
  background: var(--danger-soft);
  border-color: #e1b8b1;
  color: #7d2b22;
}

.list-heading {
  align-items: end;
}

.toolbar {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(240px, 1.4fr) repeat(2, minmax(160px, 1fr)) auto;
  gap: 12px;
  width: 100%;
}

.search-field {
  min-width: 0;
}

.table-wrap {
  overflow-x: auto;
  border: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.16);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}

table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
}

thead th {
  padding: 14px 16px;
  background: #f6f1e8;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-align: left;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

tbody td {
  padding: 16px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.14);
  vertical-align: top;
}

tbody tr:hover {
  background: #fffaf4;
}

.vehicle-main {
  display: grid;
  gap: 4px;
  min-width: 210px;
}

.vehicle-main strong {
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.vehicle-detail,
.amount-caption,
.hold-note,
.empty-state p,
.activity-meta {
  color: var(--muted);
}

.amount-block {
  display: grid;
  gap: 6px;
  min-width: 150px;
}

.amount-value {
  font-weight: 700;
}

.amount-value.positive {
  color: var(--brand);
}

.amount-value.negative {
  color: var(--danger);
}

.status-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  min-height: 32px;
  padding: 0 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 0.86rem;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
}

.status-badge.stock {
  background: var(--brand-soft);
  border-color: #badcc9;
  color: #225339;
}

.status-badge.pending {
  background: var(--accent-soft);
  border-color: #dfc0a6;
  color: #7a481d;
}

.status-badge.sold {
  background: var(--info-soft);
  border-color: #bbd7e1;
  color: #254b5a;
}

.row-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.row-actions .button {
  min-width: 84px;
  min-height: 36px;
  padding: 0 12px;
}

.empty-state {
  padding: 26px 18px;
  text-align: center;
}

.empty-state strong {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.activity-block {
  margin-top: 22px;
  padding-top: 18px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.14);
}

.subheading {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.activity-list {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: grid;
}

.activity-list li {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) auto auto;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 12px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.12);
}

.activity-list li:first-child {
  border-top: 0;
}

.activity-main {
  display: grid;
  gap: 3px;
}

.activity-main strong,
.activity-amount {
  font-weight: 600;
}

.activity-amount.negative {
  color: var(--danger);
}

.activity-amount.positive {
  color: var(--brand);
}

.sr-only {
  position: absolute;
  width: 1px;
  height: 1px;
  padding: 0;
  margin: -1px;
  overflow: hidden;
  clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
  border: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 1220px) {
  .summary-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .workspace-grid,
  .hero-band {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .toolbar {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }
}

@media (max-width: 820px) {
  .page-shell {
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .summary-grid,
  .form-grid,
  .toolbar,
  .hero-meta {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .panel {
    padding: 18px;
  }

  .panel-heading,
  .subheading {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .sale-field,
  .notes-field {
    grid-column: auto;
  }

  table,
  thead,
  tbody,
  th,
  td,
  tr {
    display: block;
  }

  thead {
    display: none;
  }

  tbody tr {
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(125, 104, 79, 0.14);
  }

  tbody td {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 110px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-top: 0;
  }

  tbody td::before {
    content: attr(data-label);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .row-actions {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .activity-list li {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
